Package domain

Class Organizacao

java.lang.Object
domain.Organizacao
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Organizacao
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Current class implements the tools for creating new organizations (as Organizacao) with specific parameters such as name (nome), tax id number (nif), website, phone number (telefone), email, address and a manager (gestor). It has implementations to get all these parameters through toString() method and a method to set the manager from an organization.
